From 59352842e68ad6d0f7e46ce52926b15d26b7ed8d Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Karthikeyan Kathirvel <kathirve@qti.qualcomm.com>
Date: Fri, 30 May 2025 11:12:13 +0530
Subject: [PATCH 4/4] wifi: ath12k: add WMI infra support for PTQM

Previous change added support to form a list having peers ready for
migration.

Add the WMI infra to send the migration command to firmware. Multiple
peers could be packed in a single WMI command. The num peers that can
be packed in a single command depends on the WMI message size. The list
formed earlier will be the input to WMI send infra.

Also, add support to handle the migration event response from the firmware.

Co-developed-by: Aditya Kumar Singh <quic_adisi@qti.qualcomm.com>
